parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rack and pinion can cause the loss of steering control, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: Clunking or popping noise when driving
loose steering
difficulty turning
vibration in the steering wheel
and sudden loss of steering control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering bolt can cause the loss of steering control, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: Sudden loss of steering control
loud clunking or snapping noise
and the steering wheel spinning freely.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the tie rod can cause the loss of steering control, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: Clunking or popping noise when driving
loose steering
difficulty turning
and sudden loss of steering control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering can cause the loss of steering control, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: Difficulty steering
heavy steering
and sudden loss of power steering assist.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the water pump can cause engine overheating, leading to engine damage or failure.
symptoms: Overheating engine
white smoke coming from the tailpipe
and loss of coolant.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the loss of vehicle control, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: Sudden loss of transmission function
difficulty shifting gears
and strange noises from the transmission.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracking of the dashboard around the passenger airbag can compromise the airbag's functionality, potentially leading to improper deployment or failure to deploy in the event of an accident, which can result in serious injury or fatality.
symptoms: Cracking or splitting of the dashboard on either side of the passenger airbag
cracks growing in size over time
and in some cases
the airbag compartment is visible.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door weather stripping can cause water to enter the vehicle, leading to damage to the electrical system, carpets, and upholstery, and potentially causing safety issues such as short circuits or electrical fires.
symptoms: Shrinking or failure of the weather stripping around the doors
water entering the vehicle
and damage to the interior.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door latch can cause the door to become stuck or difficult to open, potentially trapping occupants in the vehicle and hindering evacuation in emergency situations.
symptoms: The door latch breaks
making it difficult or impossible to open the door from the inside
and in some cases
the door can only be opened from the outside.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities, as the occupants are not properly protected.
symptoms: Airbag light flashing on and off
airbags not deploying in a crash
cracks or splits in the dashboard around the airbag housing.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Cracks or splits in the dashboard around the airbag housing can compromise the proper deployment of the airbag, leading to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Cracks or splits in the dashboard around the airbag housing
airbag light flashing on and off
concern about airbag deployment.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seats to remain in place during a rear-end collision can cause injuries or fatalities, as the occupants are not properly restrained.
symptoms: Seats reclining or moving forward during a rear-end collision
occupants thrown from their seats or injured.
